---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout
  title="About | Kreativ Sound"
  description="About Kreativ Sound, an independent sound design project creating atmospheric presets and textures."
  canonical="https://kreativsound.com/about/"
  activeNav="about"
>
  <section class="card page-main brand-page">
    <div class="brand-hero">
      <div class="brand-hero-copy">
        <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
        <h1 class="page-title">Independent sound design built around mood, clarity, and usable texture.</h1>
        <p class="page-lead">Kreativ Sound focuses on ambient, experimental, and cinematic sound materials that help creators move quickly without sacrificing identity.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="brand-hero-panel">
        <p class="product-section-kicker">What this is</p>
        <h2>A focused catalog, not a trend machine</h2>
        <p>Each release is meant to give producers, editors, and sound designers a stronger starting point: darker tone, faster workflow, and fewer generic sounds.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="brand-grid">
      <article class="product-panel product-panel-modern product-panel-accent">
        <p class="product-section-kicker">Catalog</p>
        <h2>What Kreativ Sound releases</h2>
        <p>Preset packs, sample collections, and free companion releases designed for music production, film edits, transitions, dark ambient work, and cinematic electronic sessions.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="product-panel product-panel-modern">
        <p class="product-section-kicker">Principle</p>
        <h2>Built for practical use</h2>
        <p>Every release is shaped around clear sonic identity, ready-to-use textures, and formats that fit directly into real workflows instead of sitting as abstract sound design exercises.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="product-panel product-panel-modern">
        <p class="product-section-kicker">Context</p>
        <h2>Part of the KREATIV ecosystem</h2>
        <p>Kreativ Sound sits inside the wider <a href="https://madebykreativ.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">KREATIV</a> network of independent creative tools and assets, alongside design and publishing projects with the same direct, product-led mindset.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
